{"tid":1173131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【PUBG上腦】32樓都唔驚！7童學「食雞」天台邊緣亂擒喪跳","createTime":"2019-05-27T01:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T10:14:55.000Z","uid":3090,"like":137,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd7cab2459889df3969aa801e2334147ce9acf8","tid":1173131,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2hPQUK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2hPQUK.png&h=142f5783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣東深圳有7名小學生，竟模仿俗稱「食雞」（PUBG；PlayerUnknown's Battlegrounds）的手機遊戲，在32層高大廈的天台護欄邊緣攀爬、跳躍，險象環生。<br />\n<br />\n從網民於22日拍到的影片可見，一名身穿小學生校服的男孩，在天台護欄邊緣攀爬、跳躍，沒有任何防護措施，讓人看得提心吊膽。據指，片中男孩在上演真人「食雞」，當天共有7名學生。有業主去勸阻無果，還被反駁「不關你事」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民看過影片後，紛紛留言：「感覺遊戲又要背鍋了」、「安全教育呀，安全意識早教育呀！這個風險家庭擔不起呀」、「玩命吃雞，這熊孩子。」<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"e0187a9d94813a0add4717309cf73f8bc599bf53","tid":1173131,"uid":51701,"like":215,"dislike":2,"score":213,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:56:54.000Z","msg":"支那用語好on9<br />\n<br />\n熊孩子, 屌你老母你班仆街蟲黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579b4d3719fc2afd60fd358bf60c250d79758dbd","tid":1173131,"uid":123848,"like":179,"dislike":2,"score":177,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:57:58.000Z","msg":"又掛食雞事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地玩極限運動。"},{"pid":"7594439a5b5a9d8c0a5d5eac78d831e4fcbd7030","tid":1173131,"uid":72012,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:59:20.000Z","msg":"食雞高空跌落去都會死啦"},{"pid":"48b7c5ff8cd5e914e6cc7e559ae1ee33e23dcb2f","tid":1173131,"uid":65346,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"收錢轉移引渡惡法視線"},{"pid":"60b2aa1bcddc22eca59ffb780626270800729406","tid":1173131,"uid":30109,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T02:00:27.000Z","msg":"牛B牛B"},{"pid":"50d8820611ebec4dbae40079a73f7383dbeea36a","tid":1173131,"uid":100016,